  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4d54e6da169902b4db8e974e80a3fe1a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day 1 Radio Transmission
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  delayBetweenCharacters: 0.05
  delayBetweenLines: 2
  lines:
  - ALERT TO ALL CITIZENS
  - As of a few moments ago, we have confirmed the arrival of an otherworldly presence
    enveloping the surroundings of the dome.
  - Currently, we do not understand the full scope of its capabilities but have identified
    that it has the ability to infect exposed individuals with a virus the complications
    of which we cannot yet identify.
  - We have however discovered that the virus causes a rash that may appear on either
    arm of the infected. Citizens who experience this complication must contact us
    via their computer messaging application immediately.
  - As of this moment, efforts are in progress to evacuate all citizens to a temporary
    safe location until this issue is resolved. Information regarding such can be
    found on your computer messages.
  - Precautions are in place to prevent any exterior governing figures of greater
    territories from intervening or proving as a threat to any citizens, so there
    is no need for unrest among citizens regarding this topic.
  - In order to fulfil the evacuation, all citizens are instructed to not leave their
    home without proper authorization.
  - I REPEAT, CITIZENS MAY NOT LEAVE THEIR HOME WITHOUT PROPER AUTHORIZATION.
